00:08:21,543 --> 00:08:23,336
if I'm gonna trick you.

184
00:08:23,336 --> 00:08:27,841
So, for this fight, I won't use
my specialty: Lethal Formation.

185
00:08:27,841 --> 00:08:29,342
What do you think
of that, huh?

186
00:08:29,342 --> 00:08:30,802
Wish I knew what
they were saying.

187
00:08:30,802 --> 00:08:32,137
This is intense.

188
00:08:32,137 --> 00:08:34,806
