00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,885
With a buddy call, Kanahebi
regains one life point.

221
00:09:53,885 --> 00:09:55,637
♪

222
00:09:55,637 --> 00:09:59,474
And Sniping Ninja,
Yoichi to the left!

223
00:09:59,474 --> 00:10:01,768
To top it off,
I call to the center,

224
00:10:01,768 --> 00:10:03,812
Fire Streak
Ninja, Gokuen.

225
00:10:03,812 --> 00:10:05,396
You ready, Yami?

226
00:10:05,396 --> 00:10:06,564
Hmm.

227
00:10:06,564 --> 00:10:09,734
♪

228
00:10:09,734 --> 00:10:11,736
Told ya, piece of cake.

229
00:10:11,736 --> 00:10:14,572
Okay, Yoichi, Gokuen,
the center's wide open.

230
00:10:14,572 --> 00:10:15,824
Attack the fighter!

231
00:10:15,824 --> 00:10:18,576
♪

