00:10:20,411 --> 00:10:22,038
♪

234
00:10:22,038 --> 00:10:23,331
(grunts)

235
00:10:23,331 --> 00:10:25,875
End of move.

236
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:31,005
And with that, my Cobra Crow
Poison Swamp combo is complete.

237
00:10:31,005 --> 00:10:32,382
What an exciting match!

238
00:10:32,382 --> 00:10:34,342
I can't even wait to recap!

