00:10:50,984 --> 00:10:52,318
Are you watching this?

249
00:10:52,318 --> 00:10:55,864
Seriously, it's Zanya's
turn to attack next.

250
00:10:55,864 --> 00:10:58,783
Must be this mountain air cause
everyone's talking crazy.

251
00:10:58,783 --> 00:11:01,244
Katana World's
no place for demons.

252
00:11:01,244 --> 00:11:03,538
We're better at making
traps than avoiding them.

253
00:11:03,538 --> 00:11:07,625
♪

